.TH "vmcoredd_update_program_headers" 9 "vmcoredd_update_program_headers" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmcoredd_update_program_headers \- Update all Elf program headers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" vmcoredd_update_program_headers
.BI "(char *elfptr "  ","
.BI "size_t elfnotesz "  ","
.BI "size_t vmcoreddsz "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "elfptr" 12
Pointer to elf header
.IP "elfnotesz" 12
Size of elf notes aligned to page size
.IP "vmcoreddsz" 12
Size of device dumps to be added to elf note header
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Determine type of Elf header (Elf64 or Elf32) and update the elf note size.
Also update the offsets of all the program headers after the elf note header.
